{"tid":1746650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再repost啲濕鳩文宣","createTime":"2019-11-22T23:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T00:50:27.000Z","uid":267773,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca81c6035f0d7c40ca1dc9bfdb7cbe5519427f9","tid":1746650,"uid":267773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FphY1cT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFphY1cT.png&h=35b22c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實好想講現實中幾時有分化過？<br />\n由成個運動開始之後一直啲五毛都上水做分化撚㗎啦<br />\n真正支持同參與運動既和理非根本知道大家係命運共同體...<br />\n之前仲有個手動轉聲明 話咩就算有咩唔方便都唔會埋怨示威者 我地唔會割席 一個普通香港人上... 大佬呀你自己咪示威者囉 仲要係ig呢啲係同溫層轉 根本無撚用過個腦就鳩repost <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n和理非做既野已經相對簡單 希望大家repost之前三思 都唔介意某啲人ig抗爭 但ig抗爭都比少少質素呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d2f2bf6a4f0a81a18d5ef6a9ac34b04aab0f5f","tid":1746650,"uid":39751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/FphY1cT.png\" />"},{"pid":"94cec5fcb0886e9c4ee6b2c2f27b00878c687104","tid":1746650,"uid":267773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d2f2bf6a4f0a81a18d5ef6a9ac34b04aab0f5f","tid":1746650,"uid":39751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/FphY1cT.png\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:53:12.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊個諗呢個post出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b4355398e0cec2f00d6d4931e53380d8a988d7","tid":1746650,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T23:53:43.000Z","msg":"出呢張個人想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0485b791fcffa8a5c8ca912b11b35e6e87a280","tid":1746650,"uid":267773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b4355398e0cec2f00d